  {
    "row": 10,
    "rowsha": "htY10cgeL+MQi+eSHBEaz3bCob/zRne/tu/zZb2MCnA=",
    "originContent": "`secrets` is a library to help Rust programmers safely hold cryptographic",
    "translatedContent": "`secrets` は Rust プログラマーが暗号化された秘密情報を安全にメモリに保持するのを助けるライブラリです。"
  },
  {
    "row": 11,
    "rowsha": "MSsKK6aj3LCZf/sECFQTsfWyH4bijwAvaxEhaRNS4Oo=",
    "originContent": "secrets in memory.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 12,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "これは主に [libsodium] が提供するメモリ保護ユーティリティの使いやすいラッパーです。"
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "/FfNKBYROGhY+XJBzi+lWsXDrIFK36VeueFx25EmydE=",
    "originContent": "It is mostly an ergonomic wrapper around the memory-protection utilities",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "ID+zRkSuNhRbpfui8yI/QXe3tB95FHCElRkAgq5/crQ=",
    "originContent": "provided by [libsodium].",
    "translatedContent": "スタック上に割り当てられた固定サイズのバッファは以下の保護を受けます："
  },
  {
    "row": 15,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 16,
    "rowsha": "uCXSsK6HNpsdwImVqaI5LNICicgY9Ejr/vOwVlax+q0=",
    "originContent": "Fixed-size buffers allocated on the stack gain the following protections:",
    "translatedContent": "* 基盤となるメモリに対して [`mlock(2)`][mlock] が呼び出されます"
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "* 使用されなくなったときに基盤となるメモリはゼロクリアされます"
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "vETULL5sz/4JEeaS0A9MZJB5CKIY15uzzsFTCq+oavY=",
    "originContent": "* [`mlock(2)`][mlock] is called on the underlying memory",
    "translatedContent": "* ライフスパン全体で借用されるため移動できません"
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "WtoicRkWCjnOPxP9o0aZoReFa60RZ3KBUsRGH1v45Yo=",
    "originContent": "* the underlying memory is zeroed out when no longer in use",
    "translatedContent": "* 定数時間で比較されます"
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "A621DONqY6UgmWpBIwR+0dZySVnw4j44zcPWVaHhGN8=",
    "originContent": "* they are borrowed for their entire lifespan, so cannot be moved",
    "translatedContent": "* `Debug` による表示が防止されます"
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "ruV0OeN8knWOSocrO0v551ZO+Gr6FQXKKY67QhGuQxs=",
    "originContent": "* they are compared in constant time",
    "translatedContent": "* `Clone` されることが防止されます"
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "JtlszkfZ3ZL1kck07nCOeeWmJIZrrJUfgbgCsEc0CTc=",
    "originContent": "* they are prevented from being printed by `Debug`",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "1sXvXWyqIkXuykzO3WYJ24zkmunJl5q+1jax8ArRzPU=",
    "originContent": "* they are prevented from being `Clone`d",
    "translatedContent": "固定サイズおよび可変サイズのバッファはヒープ上に割り当てられ、以下の保護を受けます："
  },
  {
    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "WkOroLy7BDSL1VDK3bPfbYsAmMPwt3fYJ54Lze5IIKs=",
    "originContent": "Fixed and variable-sized buffers can be allocated on the heap and gain",
    "translatedContent": "* 基盤となるメモリはアクティブな借用がスコープ内にない限り"
  },
  {
    "row": 26,
    "rowsha": "foGoXuXhnm/8gqkuvvct3brZEuz9yPBdYYvnu+GD7u0=",
    "originContent": "the following protections:",
    "translatedContent": "  [`mprotect(2)`][mprotect] によって読み書きから保護されます"
  },
  {
    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "* 割り当てられたメモリに対して [`mlock(2)`][mlock] が呼び出されます"
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "ndDEGodSmi2CTF1oHb2ageLZNHa8vYudlWBcnGYtgM8=",
    "originContent": "* the underlying memory is protected from being read from or written to",
    "translatedContent": "* 使用されなくなったときに基盤となるメモリはゼロクリアされます"
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "X5fKH/jrKZYAQeIMgd1NauqR4xeKDTtSk2aX1NJuV1M=",
    "originContent": "  with [`mprotect(2)`][mprotect] unless an active borrow is in scope",
    "translatedContent": "* 不正なオーバーフローとアンダーフローはアクセス不可のガードページを使って検出され、"
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "F7T1WjHiS9H05tYKB/cJlWAzzy+2awo/GozHztK5YzI=",
    "originContent": "* [`mlock(2)`][mlock] is called on the allocated memory",
    "translatedContent": "  即座にセグメンテーションフォルトとプログラムの終了を引き起こします"
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "WtoicRkWCjnOPxP9o0aZoReFa60RZ3KBUsRGH1v45Yo=",
    "originContent": "* the underlying memory is zeroed out when no longer in use",
    "translatedContent": "* メモリ解放時にカナリアを用いて短いアンダーフローによるメモリ書き込みを検出し、"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "pAp3YkpKtQpALhrsOPFm2uMAuXJX5jJlwJVGBuh9RAY=",
    "originContent": "* overflows and underflows are detected using inaccessible guard pages,",
    "translatedContent": "  セグメンテーションフォルトとプログラムの終了を引き起こします"
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "QbOhyRnrxTCZKnu+RzbWh22lnEbji2/YP8//u0bi71Q=",
    "originContent": "  causing an immediate segmentation fault and program termination",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "gHwTp5nvtgCNLdueBCzn6HaAA0LKu8p0B8YpiIV6zR8=",
    "originContent": "* short underflows that write to memory are detected when memory is",
    "translatedContent": "パニック安全性"
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "NcuhWt+2WR7xk9hJEbwsy94EYWqeZooR4iJ9MqvXpjw=",
    "originContent": "  freed using canaries, and will result in a segmentation fault and",
    "translatedContent": "------------"
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "gDCq5RWpBpoDVlOE7WQZR45UcWlu8stInqA2VhUC2dY=",
    "originContent": "  program termination",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
